ðŸ‘‰ Write a Program to calculate percentage of a given student in CBSE board exam. His marks from 5 subjects must be taken as input from the keyboard.(Marks are out of 100)

________________________________________________________________________________________

ðŸ‘‰ CODE : I wrote that you can refer 

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args){
        System.out.println("Welcome to CBSE Board percentage calculator \n");
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.println("Enter the marks of chemistry : ");
        float chemistry = sc.nextFloat();
        System.out.println("Enter the marks of physics : ");
        float physics = sc.nextFloat();
        System.out.println("Enter the marks of maths : ");
        float maths = sc.nextFloat();
        System.out.println("Enter the marks of computer : ");
        float computer = sc.nextFloat();
        System.out.println("Enter the marks of english : ");
        float english = sc.nextFloat();
        float sum = chemistry+english+maths+physics+computer;
        float percentage = (sum/500)*100;
        System.out.println("Your Percentage on the basis marks entered are : ");
        System.out.println(percentage);
    }
}
_________________________________________________________________________________________

